plot: Pete and Myka follow the trail of an artifact that seems to make people taller at first, only to cause them to get sick and die later. During the investigation, Pete gets involved with an attractive female drug company associate, who ends up suspecting Pete and Myka aren't just plain, average Secret Service agents. Meanwhile, Artie, Steve and Claudia follow up on the investigation of Brother Adrian and the missing artifacts.—Paikia
